metadata.title: 1996-1999 Bering Sea Times Series Data

creators.name: Atmospheric Research (OAR), Pacific Marine Environmental Laboratory (PMEL)

metadata.description:
During the 1996-1999 the following "Times Series Data" were collected:

21  RCM7s, 2  RCM9s, 64  MTRs, 20  Seacats, 3  Pressure guages, 3  SPAAMs
1 Weather buoy , 3024  CTDs
